l LP as a bonus. The complete contents of the album are also incorporated into an extended version of the previous collection ''[[With His Hot and Blue Guitar]]'' included in the 2012 box set ''[[Johnny Cash: The Complete Columbia Album Collection]]''.\n\n==Track listing==\n{{tracklist\n| total_length = 28:57\n\n| title1 = [[Ballad of a Teenage Queen]]\n| writer1 = [[Jack Clement]]\n| length1 = 2:13\n\n| title2 = [[There You Go (Johnny Cash song)|There You Go]]\n| writer2 = [[Johnny Cash]]\n| length2 = 2:19\n\n| title3 = [[I Walk the Line]]\n| writer3 = Cash\n| length3 = 2:46\n\n| title4 = [[Don't Make Me Go]]\n| writer4 = Cash\n| length4 = 2:31\n\n| title5 = [[Guess Things Happen That Way]]\n| writer5 = Clement\n| length5 = 1:52\n\n| title6 = [[Train of Love (Johnny Cash song)|Train of Love]]\n| writer6 = Cash\n| length6 = 2:24\n\n| title7 = [[The Ways of a Woman in Love]]\n| writer7 = [[Bill Justis]], [[Charlie Rich]]\n| length7 = 2:16\n\n| title8 = [[Next in Line (Johnny Cash song)|Next in Line]]\n| writer8 = Cash\n| length8 = 2:49\n\n| title9 = [[You're the Nearest Thing to Heaven]]\n| writer9 = Jim Atkins, Cash, Hoyt Johnson\n| length9 = 2:42\n\n| title10 = I Can't Help It\n| writer10 = [[Hank Williams]]\n| length10 = 1:49\n\n| title11 = [[Home of the Blues]]\n| writer11 = Cash, Douglas Glenn Tubb, Lillie McAlpin\n| length11 = 2:41\n\n| title12 = [[Big River (Johnny Cash song)|Big River]]\n| writer12 = Cash\n| length12 = 2:35\n}}\n{{tracklist\n| headline = Re-issue Bonus tracks\n| writer_credits = yes\n| collapsed = yes\n| total_length = 38:08\n\n| title13 = [[Don't Make Me Go]]\n| writer13 = Cash\n| length13 = 2:30\n\n| title14 = [[The Ways of a Woman in Love]]\n| writer14 = Justis, Rich\n| length14= 2:28\n\n| title15 = [[Ballad of a Teenage Queen]]\n| writer15 = Clement\n| length15 = 2:15\n\n| title16 = [[Guess Things Happen That Way]]\n| writer16 = Clement\n| length16 = 1:58\n}}\n\n==Personnel==\n*Johnny Cash&nbsp;\u2014 Vocals, acoustic Guitar and main perf